            {"speaker": "Star", "text": "Ugh... did I?", "text_cn": "呃...是吗？"},
            {"speaker": "Alex", "text": "Yeah. Get up or you'll be late for your meeting.", "text_cn": "是的，快起来不然你开会要迟到了。"},
            {"speaker": "Star", "text": "Alright, alright. I'm up. Thanks, man.", "text_cn": "好的好的，我起来了。谢谢兄弟。"},
            {"speaker": "Alex", "text": "No problem. Coffee's brewing.", "text_cn": "不客气，咖啡正在煮。"},
            {"speaker": "Star", "text": "You're a lifesaver.", "text_cn": "你真是我的救星。"}
